      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is an absolute gem\u2014spotless inside and out, and it still smells brand new. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s in truly pristine condition. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. You really have to see it to believe how well it\u2019s been kept! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
