    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered for the discerning collector is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 naturally aspirated inline-six paired with a precise ZF 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically pristine, with the critical 'Big Three' preventative measures already completed: the rear subframe has been reinforced, the VANOS system overhauled with upgraded seals, and rod bearings replaced with treated shells. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, supported by fresh OEM bushings and a perfectly calibrated variable M differential lock. With consistent paint depth across all panels and an immaculate undercarriage, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of M-division engineering in turnkey condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
